                <li class="text-subheading flex items-start gap-2">
                  <%= safe_phrase('litetracker_nesha-hero-subheader-1', "Over our 14 years of existence, we have collaborated with dozens of teams across various industries. During that time, we have had the opportunity to use multiple project management tools, such as Jira, RedMine, Github, Asana, Trello, and many others, including Pivotal Tracker. Pivotal Tracker was the tool of choice for several projects where we highly valued the responsiveness of the user experience.") %>
