                <li class="text-subheading flex items-start gap-2">
                  <%= safe_phrase('litetracker_nesha-hero-subheader-2', 'We aimed to maintain a similar essence through its successor. Our main objectives were to achieve a responsive dashboard and a user-friendly experience. I am hopeful that we will achieve complete success.') %>
